---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout>
  <section class="mb-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-brand-orange">The best things</h1>
    <blockquote class="border-l-4 pl-4 italic text-gray-500 my-8">
      <span id="recs-quote"
        >...to hedge against the terror of having a terrible memory. Though
        still young enough to expect no sympathy, I constantly feel the burden
        of this handicap. Confirmation of it, and that writing is its cure, I
        discover every time I pick up something I wrote years, or even months
        ago. Reading those things puts me in an uncanny state, like a past-life
        regression. Meanwhile, unrecorded impressions, sayings, old friends, and
        good books vanish without warning or trace. Some read and write to win
        eternal life; I would be happy enough just to keep a hold of this one.</span
      ><br />
      <span class="not-italic">– Nathan Schneider</span>
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <details class="bg-green-900 text-white rounded" open>
      <summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 text-lg font-medium"
        >Overall</summary
      >
      <div
        class="bg-white text-gray-900 rounded-b px-4 py-4 border-t border-gray-900"
      >
        <p>My favourite things per se are talking to people...</p>
        <!-- Nested dropdowns -->
        <details class="mt-4 border border-gray-200 rounded">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium bg-gray-100"
            >Free Things</summary
          >
          <div class="px-3 py-2">
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
              <li>Sneezing</li>
              <li>Libraries</li>
              <li>Cold water</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="mt-4 border border-gray-200 rounded">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium bg-gray-100"
            >Underrated Things</summary
          >
          <div class="px-3 py-2">
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
              <li>Cold Food</li>
              <li>Vocal Fry & Intentional Rasp</li>
              <li>Lemon</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="mt-2 border border-gray-200 rounded">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium bg-gray-100"
            >Overrated Things</summary
          >
          <div class="px-3 py-2">
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
              <li>Nightclubs</li>
              <li>Alcohol</li>
              <li>Coffee</li>
              <li>Smoking</li>
              <li>IYKYK Energy</li>
              <li>Acronyms</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="bg-green-900 text-white rounded">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 text-lg font-medium"
        >Writing</summary
      >
      <div
        class="bg-white text-gray-900 rounded-b px-4 py-4 border-t border-gray-900"
      >
        <details class="mt-4 border border-gray-200 rounded">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium bg-gray-100"
            >Books</summary
          >
          <div class="px-3 py-2">
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5"></ul>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="mt-4 border border-gray-200 rounded">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium bg-gray-100"
            >Videos</summary
          >
          <div class="px-3 py-2">
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
              <li>
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LCEmiRjPEtQ"
                  >Andrej Karpathy: Software Is Changing (Again)</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="mt-4 border border-gray-200 rounded">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium bg-gray-100"
            >Blogs</summary
          >
          <div class="px-3 py-2">
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
              <li><a href="https://scottaaronson.blog/">Scott Aaronson</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.jefftk.com/">Jeff Kaufman</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.benkuhn.net/">Ben Kuhn</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://tbenthompson.com/">Ben Thompson</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://simonwillison.net/">Simon Willison</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.byran.ee/">Bryan Huang</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://cpojer.net/">Christoph Nakazawa</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.linusakesson.net/">Linus Åkesson</a></li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://www.kitchensoap.com/about-me/">John Allspaw</a>
              </li>
              <li><a href="https://brooker.co.za/blog/">Marc Brooker</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://zachholman.com/posts">Zach Holmann</a></li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://carloarg02.medium.com/">Carlos Arguelles</a>
              </li>
              <li><a href="https://usesthis.com/">Many people</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://nelhage.com/">Nelson Elhage</a></li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://programmingisterrible.com/"
                  >Progamming is Terrible</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="mt-4 border border-gray-200 rounded">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium bg-gray-100"
            >Articles</summary
          >
          <div class="px-3 py-2">
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
              <li>
                <a href="https://www.benkuhn.net/progessays/"
                  >Essays on programming I think about a lot</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.sma.org.sg/UploadedImg/files/CMEP/Practice%205.pdf"
                  >Bedside Manners</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://vadimkravcenko.com/shorts/habits-of-great-software-engineers/"
                  >Habits of great software engineers</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.kitchensoap.com/2017/08/12/multiple-perspectives-on-technical-problems-and-solutions/"
                  >Multiple Perspectives on Technical Problems and Solutions</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.themarginalian.org/2013/04/17/the-art-of-conversation-martine-etiquette-1866/"
                  >The Art of Conversation: Timeless, Timely Do’s and Don’ts
                  from 1866</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/CSZnj2YNMKGfsMbZA/specializing-in-problems-we-don-t-understand"
                  >Specializing in Problems We Don't Understand</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://milan.cvitkovic.net/writing/things_youre_allowed_to_do/"
                  >Things you're allowed to do</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://www.benkuhn.net/weeklyessays/"
                  >My favourite essays of life advice</a
                >
              </li>

              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://autotranslucence.wordpress.com/2018/03/30/becoming-a-magician/"
                >
                  Becoming a Magician
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="http://johnsalvatier.org/blog/2017/reality-has-a-surprising-amount-of-detail"
                >
                  Reality has a surprising amount of detail
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://mindingourway.com/rest-in-motion/">
                  Rest in motion
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.jefftk.com/p/the-privilege-of-earning-to-give"
                >
                  The Privilege of Earning to Give
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/bjjbp5i5G8bekJuxv/study-guide"
                >
                  Study Guide
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="bg-green-900 text-white rounded">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 text-lg font-medium"
        >People</summary
      >
      <div
        class="bg-white text-gray-900 rounded-b px-4 py-4 border-t border-green-900"
      >
        <!-- Add people content here -->
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="bg-green-900 text-white rounded">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 text-lg font-medium"
        >Misc</summary
      >
      <div
        class="bg-white text-gray-900 rounded-b px-4 py-4 border-t border-gray-900"
      >
        <details class="mt-4 border border-gray-200 rounded">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium bg-gray-100"
            >Restaurants & Cafes</summary
          >
          <div class="px-3 py-2">
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5"></ul>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="mt-4 border border-gray-200 rounded">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer px-3 py-2 text-base font-medium bg-gray-100"
            >Videos</summary
          >
          <div class="px-3 py-2">
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
              <li>
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LCEmiRjPEtQ"
                  >Andrej Karpathy: Software Is Changing (Again)</a
                >
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  summary {
    background: #ff9900;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 0.375rem 0.375rem 0 0;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  details {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(20, 82, 20, 0.08);
  }
  details[open] > summary {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }
</style>
